main.name: Priyansha
main.description: I'm a passionate Full Stack Developer, currently working with Capgemini for a client Aviva as a Developer
main.bio: My name is Priyansha, I'm currently working in Capgemini. I have a profound knowledge in Technologies such as ASP.NET, C#, MVC, Azure PAAS, Javascript, React JS, Git etc with a strong communication skill. I also have a deep understanding of Agile methodolgy and have done multiple projects in this. I consider my biggest strengths as being a individual contributor, a great Team Player, always being ready for new challenges.
